<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Outcome</title>
  </head>
  <body style="background-color:powderblue;">
    <header id="main header">
    </header>
    <nav id="main menu">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/careers">Careers</a></li>
        <li><a href="/questions">Questions</a></li>
        <li><a href="/surveys">Surveys</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <section>
      <h1>Associated outcomes:</h1>
      <div>
        An outcome is a relation between this question and a particular career, it has a weight to determine how much this question
        contributes to deciding that a certain career is what really fits someone
        <br>
        List of all current outcomes for this question:
        <table border="1">
          <tr>
            <th>Outcome ID</th>
            <th>Career --> weight</th>
            <th>Delete</th>
          </tr>
          <%outcomes.map do |outcome|%>
          <tr>
            <th><%=outcome.outcome_id%></th>
            <th><a href='/outcomes/<%=outcome.outcome_id%>'><%=Career.find(career_id: outcome.career_id).name%> --> <%=outcome.weight%> </a></th>
            <th>
              <form action="outcomes/<%=outcome.outcome_id%>/delete" method="post">
                <input type="hidden" name="id" value=<%=outcome.outcome_id%>>
                <input type='submit' value='Delete'>
              </form>
            </th>
          </tr>
          <%end%>
        </table>
      </div>
      <br>
      <div>
        Add a new outcome:
        <form action="/outcomes/new" method="post">
          <ul>
            <li>
              <label for="qcareer">Career id:</label>
              <select class="" name="career">
                <%careers.map do |careers|%>
                <option value = <%=careers.career_id%> > <%=careers.name%> </option>
                <%end%>
              </select>
            </li>
            <li>
              <label for="qweight">Weighting:</label>
              <input type='number', id="qweight", name='weight' required>
            </li>
          </ul>
            <input type="hidden" id="choiceid" name="choice_id" value="<%=choice.choice_id%>">
            <input type='submit' value='Submit new outcome relation'>
            </form>
            <br>
      </div>
      <div>
        <form action="delete" method="post">
          <input type="hidden" name="id" value=<%=question.question_id%>>
          <input type="hidden" name="choice_id" value=<%=question.choice_id%>>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
    <br>
    <footer id="main footer">Â©2021 team 1. All rights reserved.</footer>
  </body>
</html>
